08835 *                                                                                             
08835C     KPMTABD       CHAIN     PMTABD                                                           
08835C                   IF        %FOUND AND PEDESC<>''                                            
08835C                   EVAL      MBWHLO=PEDESC                                                    
08835C                   ENDIF                                                                      
08835C                   ENDIF                                                                      
08835C                   Close(E)  PMTABD                                                           
08835                                                                                               
     C                   EVAL      MBITNO=Q1ARVM                                                    
     C     KMITBAL10     CHAIN     MITBAL10                                                         
     C     KZAQBAL00     CHAIN     ZAQBAL00                                                         
     C                   IF        NOT %FOUND                                                       
     C                   EVAL      MBWHLO=M9REWH                                                    
     C     KMITBAL10     CHAIN     MITBAL10                                                         
     C     KZAQBAL00     CHAIN     ZAQBAL00                                                         
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
